  "title": "Fire Arrows Ignite Fire",
  "description": "Fire Arrows set Blocks on Fire",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rCbrnHi.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white&label=DISCORD&color=%235865F2\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fire-arrows-start-fire\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/461166?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white&label=Curseforge&color=%23F16436\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fire-arrows-ignite-fire\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/fire-arrows-ignite-fire?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white&label=modrinth&color=%2300AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></p></center>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">With this mod fire arrows that land on blocks start fires. This makes for more fun and realistic gameplay.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VgiZ8EZ.gif\" width=\"508\" height=\"508\" /></p>\n</center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod either directly in-game or by editing the JSON file <code>config/firearrows.json</code> in your profile folder.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>blocksBrokenByFireArrows</b> - List of blocks that can be replaced by fire, such as air</p>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>\n",
